description: Runedragons are a collection of BRC333 dynamic ordinals: these dragons evolve and over time and may change hour by hour! This collection of 10k eggs will all hatch into Baby Runedragons before the halvening. Rarer Runedragons take longer to hatch. The top 30% will get Runes. From the SATS, eggs! From eggs, dragons! From baby dragons, the Runedragons are born!!!
name: Runedragons - A BRC333 Audio PFP Collection
